      "Hinge at the hips to dip slightly, then aggressively extend through hips, knees, and ankles.",
      "Shrug your shoulders, then pull your elbows high and outside.",
      "Drop under the bar and catch it in a front-rack position with elbows high.",
      "Stand up from the receiving position."
